Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this drawing of?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't recognise yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... is... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It is a drawing of ****!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:49.52,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(400,3000)\fsp2\b1\blur0\fs42\pos(368,194)\t(1000,3000,\blur3)}Time of Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:01:01.12,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\b1}Dad returns!\N{\b0}Sunday Lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yes... complainants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll tell him... yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there so many complaints?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, whenever new models were released, there would be mountains of complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many users become irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because unlike today, the AI did not have fuzzy logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Sammy. Something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would an after-meal green tea be satisfactory?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it can respond appropriately, even to an ambiguous command.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In earlier days, this was not possible.
