Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I got irritated and rejected the questions, it would get an error and freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about the old times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... But there {\i1}have{\i0} been a strange many complainants recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones that want to prohibit the use of Houseroids,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or want us to pay their collection costs in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:49.81,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Currently, the Ethics Committee is...
