Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:52.71,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx66.25\fscy97.5\pos(209,264)\frz342.3\frx8\fry22}Vagrant robots may have damaged patterns of thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:52.71,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...conducting a voluntary recall of robots which have been disconnected from their Masters' control and neglected...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That AI seems to be quite an amazing invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:01:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, the one which is like a genius scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The versions are being upgraded so quickly, we'd be able to buy something identical one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, but the return costs are becoming very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there seems to be a way of avoiding payment and getting away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Houseroid at Satou's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cute model...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you I'm not interested like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, don't surprise me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I've got some things to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be always busy recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well how do I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere noisy, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there are no customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is a strange shop, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In various ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Ms. Nagi... Why do you work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just call me "Nagi".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also like the people who come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So on days like today, when I can't see the faces of those guests I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... we...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... can I get a refill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just bring out the beans. Please wait a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is quiet, isn't it?
