Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.81,0:03:34.02,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\c&HF0F3FF&\3c&HBAC2ED&\fs28\fnAkbar\move(354,112,354,122,0,4404)}In this shop,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.81,0:03:34.02,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\c&HD5D5FF&\3c&HBEBDFD&\fnAkbar\move(355,165,355,171,0,4404)}there is no discrimination
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.81,0:03:34.02,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\c&HD5D5FF&\3c&HBEBDFD&\fnAkbar\move(354,229,354,233,0,4404)}between humans and robots.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.81,0:03:34.02,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\c&HD5D5FF&\fnAkbar\3c&H827FFD&\move(359,328,356,323,0,4404)}Customers, please cooperate.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.81,0:03:34.02,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord2\be1\fs28\fnAkbar\c&HCDCCFF&\3c&H7479DB&\move(359,406,358,392,0,4404)}Obey the rule and have a fun time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the LUH model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Houseroid model which came out around the time we were in primary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still around huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not very popular back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were many complaints that it was hard to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be shaking pretty badly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.46,Sign-Sans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(1000,0)\fsp1\c&H6E6C71&\pos(359,269)}- Doll of Eve -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some business here? We are just customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what a "customer" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am also a "customer".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Masaki. This guy is Rikuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, {\i1}humans{\i0} introduce themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduction is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:05:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a process wherein I communicate my name, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.93,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is trying to imitate humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, it's abiding by the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It is a drawing of ****!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am called... ****.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you cover your ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do not communicate my name,\Nthe introduction process cannot be concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I will be unable to verify my status as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is ****.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's alright! You don't have to overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overdo what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The introduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that? Just now, Mr. Masaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.51,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, humans introduce themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaki! This one cannot deal with fuzzy interactions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if we don't let introduce itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, we'll have to bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry! Go ahead and say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said... I am ****.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a nice name huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very important name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where might the restroom be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that broken part...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been left alone until it became like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be returned to the maker for repairs{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.70,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about those things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, one would expect, in this day and age{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.45,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikuo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already understand that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who comes here is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. What would you like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be able to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something new afterall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order! This, one more cup of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to order what Mr. Rikuo is having.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, two Evlends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to drink the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be pushing it with three cups...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I meant the robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mouth is just a speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it tries to imitate humans and drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up! The third law prohibits robot suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:22.92,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(253,102)}The Three Laws of Robotics
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:22.92,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\bord2.5\fs32\pos(304,221)}Third Law
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:22.92,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(95,325)\b1\bord2.5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}A robot must protect its own existence as long as such protection\N{\fs28}does not conflict with the First or Second Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this guy not understand that drinking could be dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is true. It couldn't possibly... be drinking... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting on the Evlend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the customer to drink, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Order! Just order it to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop the cup! It's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.79,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the customer to drink, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.33,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of age? This year I will be eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably means that he was manufactured eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought I was a bit big to be an eight-year-old human, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mr. Masaki, it was written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you only concerned about this sort of detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am eight years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a conflict between logic and the rule. It cannot answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well! There are many types of eight year olds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other eight-year-old humans who look like me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are in existence, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not have data about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-T-There's a frequent visitor to this store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there is someone who comes to this store, who is eight years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She... She's called Chie! Well, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.74,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(103,184)}8 Years
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years old... not quite that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.49,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(50,184)}Not quite eight years
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! She's big! Like, her voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing is that it's believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped with childcare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh... Childcare huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. At that place with the parents and their only son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.21,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Help me out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough does this by myself... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.72,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was all that hard work for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The danger has passed... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Where might Nagi be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was looking after her during her nap,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird is sitting there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie, let's go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.19,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's called Chie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Chie the one who is not quite eight years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person! This is Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.35,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one here is a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's just her favourite line{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.04,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just call her a cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it herself, so let's leave it at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I. Am. A. Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I will escort you to the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presently, the data is very complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you alright...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weird thing fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... is there any way I can help{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Can it be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is already{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.66,Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rikuo-kun. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here, let's have a good chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, so, you've always been working at that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That was my place of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tasked with looking after the son, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now, he has grown to a stage where I'm no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That job, did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son bestowed a name upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even now, I remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child's name! What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,**** was his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that family's surname?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their address... contact details?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful that you asked about my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who comes here is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... called me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...name... don't... forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It is a drawing of Katoran!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was illegally abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a new one is bought, the old one should be returned to the maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The collection fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they didn't want to pay it, they deleted their personal information...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This child, you see, wanted someone to remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its own name...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it has been evading the Ethics Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably didn't even know it's own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably erased as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like a robot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even having lost something ages ago, it did not realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It remained in this child's heart the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time when it received its name, those precious memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart? What do you mean heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You often said so yourself, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Because it doesn't have a heart, it doesn't understand music."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to stay there blubbering?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:47.78,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&}Vagrant Robot Report Form
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're also carrying out disposals of vagrant robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ethics Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean I was doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really ignoring us huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sammy is like that at home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it only different at that café?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Affection is not something they hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.62,Sign-Serif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(600,0)\fs32\pos(361,166)}Preview
